creator: Instied India Pvt. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Financial Calendar is here to make your Indian financial related due dates easy, sorted and you bet – “Customized”.

Financial calendar lets you search the due dates for compliances under various statutes like Income Tax, GST, ESIC, Company Law and PF.

The number of laws governing business in India is numerous. With this app, you get to navigate through the several laws in India and customize your compliance calendar depending on what laws you have got to comply with.

You select the laws and the app will customize your compliance calendar for you.

FINANCIAL CALENDAR FEATURES:
• Interface: Elegant and easy to use interface makes it super simple to get a quick overview of the upcoming events and tasks. You always keep your focus on what's important.
• Live & quick updates: Our experienced and expert personnel are live on the track to keep updating the due dates on a real-time basis. Every time you hear of new return or extension in the date etc. “You know where to go”!
• Customized Notifications: The app will not bug you with a hoard of unwanted notifications. When you select laws governing your company, notifications are customized around the selected statutes only. So you will only know what you need to know.
• Dual Theme: Both dark and light themes are supported.

Since it is entirely based on the regulatory environment of a country, due dates currently provide the compliance calendar suitable for Indian regulatory environment.

descriptionHtml:
FilingHour / Filing Hour provides all kinds of professional services at the lowest possible prices without any compromise in the service quality.

FilingHour / Filing Hour is India’s only aggregator App exclusively for professional services.

FilingHour / Filing Hour provides a wide range of services including Income Tax return filing, GST return filing, incorporation services, Trademarks, Patents, Copyright services, GST Advisory, GST Cancellation, etc.

Our prices for various products are at rock bottom inclusive of government fees. An illustrative list of the Prices of various services are the follows :

Incorporation services:
1. Private Limited Company incorporation at just 8,999
2. LLP incorporation at 6,999
3. One Person Company incorporation at 5,999
4. Nidhi Company incorporation at 31,999
5. Partnership Firm incorporation at 4,449

Income Tax returns filings include filing of income from various sources :
1. Salary / Pension
2. House Property
3. Business / Profession
4. Capital Gains
5. Other Sources
6. Foreign Income
Our system defines the prices based on the combination of the income selected and at the least possible price

GST Services includes :
1. GST Registration
2. GST Return Filing
3. GST Annual Return (GSTR – 9)
4. GST Audit (GSTR 9C)
5. GST Advisory
The prices of the GST services start from as low as 499

Trademark services and prices as follows :
1. Trademark Registration – at 5999 inclusive of taxes
2. Trademark Objection - at 2999 inclusive of taxes
3. Trademark Opposition - at 3999 inclusive of taxes
4. Trademark Renewal - at 11999 inclusive of taxes
5. Copyrights Registration
6. Design Registration
7. Patent Registration


Apart from the professional services, FilingHour / Filing Hour is also famous for its Due date calendar / the compliance calendar updated regularly. The updates are real-time and are TAT time for the update is maintained at as low as one day.

FilingHour / Filing Hour also makes your due dates easy, sorted, and you bet "Customized".

FilingHour / Filing Hour lets you search the due dates for compliances under various statutes like Income Tax, GST, Company Law, and PF.

The number of laws governing a business in India is numerous. With FilingHour / Filing Hour you get to navigate through the several laws in India and customize your compliance calendar depending on what laws you have got to comply with.

You select the laws and we will customize your compliance calendar for you and much more for “FREE”.

WHAT MAKES COMPLIANCE CALENDAR GREAT
• Interface: Elegant and easy to use interface makes it super simple to get a quick overview of the upcoming events and tasks. You always keep your focus on what's important; there is nothing to distract you
• Day, Week, Month, and List views of your events: Calendar illustrates your Day, Week, and Month on a Phone screen the best possible way. Depending on the situation, select the view that conveniently unveils your schedule.
• View returns & forms: Gives a quick insight into the returns and forms to be complied with under various laws;
• The fastest Sync: Sync with new updates works fast and keeps your schedule thoroughly
• Live & quick updates: Our experienced and expert personnel are live on the track to keep updating the due dates on a real-time basis. Every time you hear of a new return/extension in the date etc. “You know where to go”!
• Customized Notifications: We will not bug you with a hoard of unwanted notifications. When you select laws governing your company, notifications are customized around the selected statutes only. So you will only know what you need to know.

Since it is entirely based on the regulatory environment of a country, due dates currently provide the compliance calendar suitable for the Indian regulatory environment.

Reach us at support@instied.com
